{"tid":1544450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港紙兌外幣精選","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T01:20:38.000Z","uid":214784,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"948337d3142153828fa85c37af64ed93c95cb4d5","tid":1544450,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"除咗唱美金之外，其實仲有兩個選擇(可能正過美金添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n1.英鎊<br />\n預測：先跌後升<br />\n條件：約翰遜硬脫歐&rarr;跌&rarr;初期歐洲金融總部會撤出英國&rarr;再跌&rarr;隔多一陣嗰環境氣氛成熟翻就會升翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.日元<br />\n預測：慢升<br />\n條件：2020東京奧運，大日本帝國復甦；經濟活動嘅節奏會隨著奧運嚟臨而變得活躍，外國遊客越嚟越多，同時亦都可以刺激日本本土經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e430603f78591cf1c90dd4a9f5c4933394ad5f45","tid":1544450,"uid":45753,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆你個街上年11月YEN岩岩好7 依家7.4 <br />\n1月仲要去真係兌定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc292769c98fd141b5bb634f31ee39bb3ea81744","tid":1544450,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:36:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91jFMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91jFMP.gif&h=6056e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:00pm 